lead_paragraph: Rafa Nadal's below-par season has continued with the former world number one dumped from the Rio Open semi-finals with a 6-7(6) 7-6(3) 6-4 defeat by unseeded Uruguayan Pablo Cuevas on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Nadal Dumped From Rio Semi-Finals by Uruguayan Battler
